27#ifndef DEV_H
28#define DEV_H
29
30// dev plugin setup
31struct dev {
32 const char *name;
33 int (*initialized)(const char *);
34 int (*listening)(void);
35 int (*handle_device)(void *);
36 int (*start)(void);
37 void (*stop)(void);
38};
39
40struct dev_dhcpcd {
41 int (*handle_interface)(void *, int, const char *);
42};
43
44int dev_init(struct dev *, const struct dev_dhcpcd *);
45
46// hooks for dhcpcd
47#ifdef PLUGIN_DEV
48#include "dhcpcd.h"
49int dev_initialized(struct dhcpcd_ctx *, const char *);
50int dev_listening(struct dhcpcd_ctx *);
51int dev_start(struct dhcpcd_ctx *);
52void dev_stop(struct dhcpcd_ctx *);
53#else
54#define dev_initialized(a, b) (1)
55#define dev_listening(a) (0)
56#define dev_start(a) {}
57#define dev_stop(a) {}
58#endif
59
60#endif
